### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = seu_token_jwt_aqui

### 1. Listar todas as avaliações
GET {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Listar avaliações com filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes?page=1&limit=10&trimester=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Obter avaliação por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/uuid-da-avaliacao
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Criar nova avaliação
POST {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "school_id": "uuid-da-escola",
  "academic_year_id": "uuid-do-ano-academico",
  "class_id": "uuid-da-turma",
  "subject_id": "uuid-da-disciplina",
  "teacher_id": "uuid-do-professor",
  "assessment_type_id": "uuid-do-tipo-avaliacao",
  "name": "Teste de Matemática - 1º Trimestre",
  "description": "Teste sobre álgebra e geometria",
  "date": "2024-04-15",
  "trimester": 1
}

### 5. Actualizar avaliação
PUT {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/uuid-da-avaliacao
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste de Matemática - Actualizado",
  "description": "Nova descrição do teste",
  "date": "2024-04-20",
  "trimester": 1
}

### 6. Eliminar avaliação
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/uuid-da-avaliacao
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Listar notas de uma avaliação
GET {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/uuid-da-avaliacao/grades
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Guardar/Actualizar notas
POST {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/uuid-da-avaliacao/grades
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grades": [
    {
      "student_id": "uuid-do-estudante-1",
      "score": 15.5,
      "remarks": "Bom desempenho"
    },
    {
      "student_id": "uuid-do-estudante-2",
      "score": 18.0,
      "remarks": "Excelente trabalho"
    },
    {
      "student_id": "uuid-do-estudante-3",
      "score": 12.0,
      "remarks": "Precisa melhorar"
    }
  ]
}

### 9. Listar pautas
GET {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/sheets/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Listar pautas com filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/sheets/list?class_id=uuid-da-turma&status=submitted
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Criar pauta
POST {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/sheets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "school_id": "uuid-da-escola",
  "academic_year_id": "uuid-do-ano-academico",
  "class_id": "uuid-da-turma",
  "subject_id": "uuid-da-disciplina",
  "trimester": 1
}

### 12. Submeter pauta (Professor)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/sheets/uuid-da-pauta/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Aprovar pauta (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes/sheets/uuid-da-pauta/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
